119
00:06:12,816 --> 00:06:16,618
So in Uncharted 4, we decided to dip our toe in the water a little bit.

120
00:06:17,461 --> 00:06:20,122
So there was the Madagascar level, which was massive,

121
00:06:20,122 --> 00:06:22,442
with some wide exploratory loops.

122
00:06:22,442 --> 00:06:24,403
But ultimately, we funneled you along this linear path.

123
00:06:24,403 --> 00:06:28,464
And then there was also the At Sea chapter.

124
00:06:28,464 --> 00:06:31,265
Massive, lots of places to wander,

