00:22:48,495 --> 00:22:50,056
Oi!

486
00:22:50,056 --> 00:22:52,497
Well, you made it across at least.

487
00:22:52,497 --> 00:22:52,617
Sorry.

488
00:22:52,617 --> 00:22:56,379
I'm sure you can find your way over here.

489
00:22:56,379 --> 00:22:58,600
Oh, definitely.

